items.name: GuildScout
items.description: GuildScout is a powerful backend service for deep analytics of activity and user behavior in Discord guilds. Using Prisma ⚙️, Node.js and Kafka 🚀, it transforms raw Discord API data into structured, valuable metrics. Ideal for server owners, analysts and community managers who want to understand their community dynamics. 📈

items.name: RLRIS
items.description: This project implements a Deep Q-Network (DQN) for optimizing Reconfigurable Intelligent Surface (RIS) configurations in 6G wireless communication systems. The system uses reinforcement learning to automatically select optimal RIS phase configurations to maximize signal quality and user fairness.
